---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE, tel } from '../config/site';

const today = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' });
---
<BaseLayout title={`Privacy Policy — ${SITE.company}`} description={`Privacy Policy for ${SITE.company}.`} noindex>
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">&larr; Back to home</a>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {today}</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        <strong>Template notice:</strong> This is a generic template and not legal advice. Privacy
        obligations vary by jurisdiction (e.g. GDPR, CCPA/CPRA). Have this policy reviewed by qualified
        counsel and tailored to your data practices before publishing.
      </div>

      <p>
        {SITE.company} ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what
        information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have when you use our website and
        submit your information through our forms.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> name, email address, phone number, and any details you include in a form.</li>
        <li><strong>Automatically collected data:</strong> basic technical data such as browser type and pages visited, where applicable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To contact you about your inquiry by phone, email, or SMS, consistent with the consent you provided.</li>
        <li>To provide, improve, and personalize our services.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Share Information</h2>
      <p>
        We may share your information with service providers who help us operate our business (such as
        form-handling, communications, and CRM providers). We do not sell your personal information
        except as disclosed to you. We may disclose information when required by law.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Your Choices &amp; Rights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Opt out of marketing texts by replying STOP; opt out of calls or emails by request.</li>
        <li>Request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information.</li>
        <li>Depending on your location, you may have rights under laws such as the GDPR or CCPA/CPRA.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Retention &amp; Security</h2>
      <p>
        We retain personal information only as long as necessary for the purposes described here or as
        required by law, and use reasonable safeguards to protect it. No method of transmission or
        storage is completely secure, however.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes are effective when posted to this page.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        To exercise your rights or ask questions, contact {SITE.company} at
        <a href={tel()}>{SITE.phoneDisplay}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
